What does it need heavy cream for? I added a bit of Earth Balance Margarine (which is nice and buttery - you can try 2 tablespoons of butter), and the full flavor of the carrots comes right through. My friend brought over a handful of fresh arugula from his garden, and it was a nice touch.

Rating: 3
I enjoy carrot puree very much so was anxious to try this recipe. I did pass on the garlic at the last minute and went by my usual dried dill. If you are not a garlic fan try this with dill. I also use fat free half and half instead of cream. I agree with the other reviews that you need to at least double the recipe.

