Rating: 3
I made this soup for Sunday dinner with a salad and hot rolls, and it was delicious. I will definitely make it again, but I would triple or even quadruple the ingredients if you want leftovers. I doubled the recipe here and it made 2 small servings. My other observation is that it was a little too salty, even using low sodium chicken broth and unsalted butter. I would cut the amount of salt in half next time. Also, to reduce the fat content, I used whole milk instead of cream and it was still very delicious. Simple and worth trying!

